<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (tʿạly̱ mạtkwnsẖ bʿyd .. ạ̹frḥ wbqlb jdyd)2
 rnm ạ̉ʿẓm nsẖyd .. (ạ̹wʿy̱ tml ạlṣlạẗ)2
 ạlqrạr- (tạ̉jylk msẖ hạyfyd)2 .. (wʿnạdk lyh wyạh)2
 2- (tʿạly̱ dh ạlbạb mftwḥ .. ạ̹smʿ lklạm ạlrwḥ)2
 dh yswʿ ʿnk mjrwḥ .. (ygẖsl ạ̹tẖmk bdmạh)2
 3- (tʿạly̱ wblạsẖ tạ̉jyl .. ạ̹kẖḍʿ lṣwt ạlạ̹njyl)2
 tḥlạlk ạltrạtyl .. (tmtly mn rwḥ ạllh)2
 4- (tʿạly̱ sẖạyl ạlṣlyb .. wạtbʿ fạdynạ ạlḥbyb)2
 dh rjạʾk msẖ hạykẖyb .. (ạ̹n ʿsẖt ḥsb wṣạyạh)2
 5- (tʿạly̱ kẖlyk shrạn .. wạḥml trs ạlạ̹ymạn)2
 thzm jns ạlsẖyṭạn .. (bạlṣwm wyạ ạlṣlạẗ)2</lyrics>
<title>tʿạly̱ mạtkwnsẖ bʿyd</title>
</song>